Eikena Daudi iltung'ana

(
1   Int 
21  .
1  -
27  )


1  Neitoki engoro o Laitoriani ayupuyup te nkaraki Israel, nepik Daudi endamunoto te nkaraki ninche, ejo, “Shomo nkena Israel o Yuda.” 
2  Neaku etiaka olaiguanani Yoab o lkituaak le njore, apa ootii te nebo ninye, “Enchom atua iloshon pooki le Israel, ebaiki Dan o metabaiki Beer-sheba, ninkenikene iltung'ana, pee atum atayiolo esiana oo ltung'ana.” 
3  Kake etiaka Yoab olaiguanani, “Metoponai Olaitoriani Enkai ino iltung'ana katitin iip aa kumok anaa enaba, eton edolita nkonyek o lkitok lai olaiguanani; kake kainyoo pee eshipakino olkitok lai olaiguanani ena bae?” 
4  Kake etune ororei lo laiguanani te Yoab o too lkituaak le njore. Neaku eshomo Yoab o lkituaak le njore te ine netii olaiguanani aapuo aaiken iltung'ana. 
5  Nelang ninche Yordan, neiteru abaiki Aroer, o ebaiki ina anasa natii atua empolos o erata, te nkalo e Gad nelo Yaser. 
6  Neitoki aapuonu Gilead, o Kadesh ti atua enkop oo Lhiti; nepuonu ninche Dan, nepuo te Dan nemanaa aapuo Sidon, 
7  nepuonu enkisudoroto e Turo o nkang'itie oo Lhafi o Lkanaani; neipang ninche aapuo Negeb e Yuda te Beer-sheba. 
8  Neaku ore ake pee eidip ninche aashom enkop pooki, nepuonu ninche Yerusalem te nkiting'oto oo lapaitin ooudo o nkolong'i tikitam. 
9  Neisho Yoab esiana e nkikenata oo ltung'ana olaiguanani: ore ti atua Israel netii nkalifuni iip isiet oopi oo tushututua ilalema, ore iltung'ana le Yuda naa nkalifuni iip imiet.


10  Neitanyamal Daudi oltau lenye ena kata eidipa aikena iltung'ana. Nejoki Daudi Olaitoriani, “Ataasa nanu eng'oki sapuk tena nataasa. Kake ore taata, Olaitoriani, aatoomono nanu iyie, iwuang'ie entorroni to sinka lino; amu ataasa nanu te modai.” 
11  Ore ake pee einyototo Daudi tadekenya, nelotu ororei lo Laitoriani enetii oloiboni oji Gad, ilo aduani le Daudi, ejo, 
12  “Shomo tiaaki Daudi, ‘Nji ejo Olaitoriani, ntokitin uni nanu aaisho; tegelu nabo te ninche, pee aatum aitaasa iyie.’ ” 
13  Neaku eewuo Gad enetii Daudi neliki ninye, nejoki ninye, “Kailarin okuni lo lameyu oopuonu atua enkop ino. Arashu impirri iyie ilapaitin okuni te dukuya ilmang'ati linono kisujita ninche? Arashu te neaku nkolong'i uni ino lmeitai ti atua enkop ino? Nguanare taata, nidut ewalata nashukoki nanu ilo laairiwua.” 
14  Nejoki Daudi Gad, “Atii nanu atua osina sapuk; matabatatakinoto iyiook enkaina o Laitoriani, amu kitok olng'ur lenye, kake mikincho abatatakino enkaina e tungani.”


15  Neaku eirriwaka Olaitoriani Israel olmeitai ebaiki tadekenya o metabaiki enkata apa natudung'uoki; neye te ine iltung'ana ebaiki Dan o metabaiki Beer-sheba nkalifuni ntomoni naapishana. 
16  Ore ake pee eitorioo olmalaika enkaina enye aing'orie Yerusalem pee eidaikie, neirridu Olaitoriani ina torroni, nejoki ilo malaika apa oasita ina mutata ti atua iltung'ana, “Eidipe; tushuko taata enkaina ino.” Netii apa ilo malaika lo Laitoriani embata ewueji neidong'ishoreki e Arauna Olyebusi. 
17  Neirorie Daudi Olaitoriani ina kata pee edol ilo malaika apa oarita iltung'ana, nejo, “Oi, ataasa nanu eng'oki, nataasa entorroni; kake amaa kuna kerra, kaa etaasa ninche? Nchoo enkaina ino, aatoomono, aar nanu near enkaji e papa.”


18  Nelotu Gad ina olong enetii Daudi, nejoki ninye, “Shomo ilepa, tataaniki olperere lo lasar enetii Olaitoriani te ine wueji neidong'ishoreki e Arauna o Ljebusi.” 
19  Neaku eshomo Daudi ailep to rorei le Gad, anaa enaitanapishe olaiguanani. 
20  Ore ake eing'orisho Arauna airrugo, nedol olaiguanani o sinkan lenyena epuonu aayiaya ninye; nelo Arauna, neserem olaiguanani neitabaiki enkomom enye enkop. 
21  Nejo Arauna, “Kainyoo pee eewuo olkitok lai olaiguanani enetii osinka lenye?” Nejo Daudi, “Pee ainyiang'u ene wueji neidong'ishoreki te iyie pee atum ateshetaki olperere lo lasar lo Laitoriani, pee etumi aaiwuang'ie olmeitai too ltung'ana.” 
22  Nejoki Arauna Daudi, “Nchoo olkitok lai olaiguanani eya neishoru ina nadol aa sidai te ninye; noolo ilmong'i lo lasar opejori, ore ntokitin naaidong'ishoreki o nkeek oo lmong'i naa keaku ilkeek. 
23  Ore kuna pooki, olaiguanani, eishoo Arauna olaiguanani.” Nejoki Arauna olaiguanani, “Mikitang'amai iyie Olaitoriani Enkai ino.” 
24  Kake etiaka olaiguanani Arauna, “A-a, kake kainyiang'u nanu te iyie te nkinyang'a; maishoru nanu olasar opejori to Laitoriani eitu nanu ainosie toki.” Neaku einyiang'ua Daudi ine wueji neidong'ishoreki, o lmong'i te shekeli onom e nkosholai. 
25  Neshetaki Daudi te ine Olaitoriani olperere lo lasar, neishoru olasar opejori o lasar le seriani. Neaku etoning'o Olaitoriani eomonokinoto enkop, neiwuang'ieki olmeitai aaitung'uaa Israel.

